141
00:10:56,948 --> 00:10:58,370
We just met.

142
00:10:58,533 --> 00:11:00,706
- Another time, then.
- No. no, no, no.

143
00:11:01,202 --> 00:11:03,421
We would love to join you and your
wife for dinner, wouldn't we?

144
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:05,082
