- Abby.

145
00:11:05,665 --> 00:11:06,791
Abby.

146
00:11:09,419 --> 00:11:10,420
What's going on, Jim?

147
00:11:10,587 --> 00:11:12,430
Start running preliminary tests
on the flower.

148
00:11:12,589 --> 00:11:14,557
